        <p class="mb-4">We offer several towel formats to match different use cases and event types. Rally towels are the most popular format for sports teams and fan merchandise, they are compact, lightweight, and easy to wave, throw, and hand out to fans at games and events, and for a complete fan merchandise package our <a href="/custom-apparel/group-wear/spirit-wear-shirts" class="link-notification">spirit wear</a> shop produces coordinating team shirts and hoodies in the same order. Full beach towels and sport towels offer more surface area for complex full-color artwork and are preferred for premium corporate gifts, gym merchandise, and team gear that will be used extensively outside of event settings, and many gym and fitness clients pair their towel orders with <a href="/custom-apparel" class="link-notification">custom apparel</a> so members get a coordinated branded experience across their gear.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">For gyms and fitness studios throughout the Chicagoland area, branded sport towels are a practical and appreciated merchandise offering that members use at every workout. A quality branded gym towel that a member uses daily is one of the most consistent brand touchpoints any fitness business can offer, and for gyms that also want branded event bags our <a href="/promotional-items/tote-bags" class="link-notification">custom tote bags</a> pair with towels in a member welcome kit that sets the tone from day one. We produce custom gym towels with full-color logos that remain vibrant through countless washing cycles.</p>
        <p>We have no minimums on custom towel orders and can accommodate both small personal orders and large commercial quantities. Design help is available for organizations that need assistance creating artwork that works well at full towel scale. Call us at (815) 349 8600 or visit 121 Springfield Avenue in Joliet to discuss your custom towel project today.</p>
